Issue #1

Problem  : conditional html when form error not working
Reason   : was checking the wrong $_GET variable
Solution : changed $_GET variable to 'error'

Issue #2

Problem  : email check function not returning int of how many records exist with target email
Reason   : i was using the 'select' function of my database class when i should have been using 'count'
Solution : Use 'count' instead of 'select'

Issue #3

Problem  : password dont need to match for the password checking function to return true
Reason   : i passed the same variable twice to the function by mistake
Solution : change the second variable to the correct password variable

Issue #4

Problem  : Item Links have the wrong item id assigned
Reason   : sql inner join overwriting id value for the product
Solution : adjust sql statement

Issue #5

Problem  : input sanitization wasnt working
Reason   : using wrong anitise function
Solution : changed function to htmlspecialchars()